decks.notes: The key concept of this deck revolves around utilizing the control elements of blue and white to disrupt opponents and protect your board while establishing a strong aggressive presence. The deck is designed to maintain a balance between countering and removing threats, while also deploying aggressive creatures to apply pressure and close out the game quickly. It features strong counterspells like Mana Leak and Force of Will, as well as efficient removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Oust. The inclusion of powerful planeswalkers such as Teferi, Time Raveler and Jace, the Mind Sculptor further enhances the control and card advantage aspects of the deck. Overall, the deck aims to control the game until it can launch aggressive assaults and secure victory.

The key concept of this deck is to aggressively attack opponents with Kelsien, the Plague as the commander. The deck focuses on generating value through powerful creatures and disruptive spells. It includes a mix of removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Lightning Bolt, as well as disruptive creatures like General Kudro of Drannith and Tithe Taker. The deck also includes cards like Ravenloft Adventurer and Robber of the Rich to generate card advantage and resources from the opponent's decks. Additionally, the deck utilizes a variety of lands to ensure consistency in mana production. Overall, the goal is to establish an aggressive board presence while disrupting the opponent's game plan.
